posts.title: WAKING UP AT 4 am tomorrow...going to open the Polls at 5 am I am doing my part as a Supervisor to watch over the process. My job includes also closing the polls and making certain every ballot is secured - locked and loaded into a bag that is sealed....then handed off to the chain of command
posts.content: I have been working the polls for a while now. During the last Primary it was my first time as being a supervisor. I now know how votes get lost. I was working with another Supervisor...let's call him Bill. He was asked if someone was registered as they did not give the right address would still be able to cast a vote. this mope started to say...YES...of course that did not fly I shut that down and dealt with the voter.....The poll workers look to us for verification and other issues that come up. I am fortunately teamed with him again..I said fortunately because he will be working with me and I will be over his shoulder and no tom foolery.....Don't be a Bill....other fellow supervisors out there...keep your eyes open....we want to ensure this will be an honest and fair election.....DO YOUR PART LIKE THE COUNTRY IS COUNTING ON YOU to CALL OUT WRONG DOING.... TRUMP 2024...
